&lt;li&gt;Identifies appropriate business outcomes and connects them to go-to-market initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates attention to detail, is highly organized, and able to manage multiple projects under tight deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborates effectively with diverse cross-functional teams and helps to manage various projects; including action item tracking, delivering project status updates, and stakeholder communications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigates ambiguity and makes thoughtful recommendations by identifying key assumptions and leveraging available information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for technology and interest in the intersection of marketing and product development. A big plus for those with Okta and/or Auth0 product familiarity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
