&lt;p&gt;We are looking to hire&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;two &lt;/strong&gt;Customer First Strategy and Operations Interns. In this role, you will gain hands-on experience working with Okta’s Customer Success and Renewals Operations teams. This role provides exposure to key areas, including sales process optimization, sales systems, customer success and renewals strategy and operations. You’ll work closely with cross-functional teams, analyze data to drive business insights, and support initiatives that enhance operational efficiency across Okta’s go-to-market strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
