&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;After 90 days of active employment, interns are eligible for medical, dental, and vision insurance. We cover 100% of employee premiums under at least one medical plan and 80% of dependent premiums&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
