 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Zone 3 (Lake Mary, FL; Clearwater, FL; Gainesville, FL)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$28&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$28 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;a href=&quot;https://careers.robinhood.com/benefits&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to learn more about our Total Rewards, which vary by region and entity.&lt;/p&gt;
